5ï¸âƒ£ Russian Doll Caching (Advanced but impressive)

	Nested fragment caching.

	<% cache @post do %>
	  <% @post.comments.each do |comment| %>
	    <% cache comment do %>
	      <%= comment.body %>
	    <% end %>
	  <% end %>
	<% end %>


	Only updated parts expire.

	ğŸ“Œ Say:

	â€œRails supports Russian doll caching for efficient partial updates.â€



