7ï¸âƒ£ How Rails Reads/Writes Cache Internally (Good follow-up)

	Rails serializes objects (usually Marshal)

	Stored in cache store

	On read:

	If hit â†’ return cached value

	If miss â†’ execute block â†’ store result

